LinShare

Specially designed to allow secure file exchange for companies that put privacy and
traceability in the heart of their collaboration strategy, LinShare provides a
simple and intuitive solution.

    * Linshare allows employees to upload files into their space,
    * Linshare can share files with internal or external collaborators,
    * Linshare offers various features for secure file exchange

More information at http://www.linshare.org/

